  <summary date="2019-08-16T13:44:13Z" status="Introduced in House">Pink Tax Repeal Act 

This bill prohibits product manufacturers or service providers from selling substantially similar products at different prices based on the gender of the intended purchaser. If, for example, the only difference between two products is the color, they are substantially similar.</summary>
